        Amendment, by leave, withdrawn.
      </p>
      <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_436gc' title='Col. 436GC &mdash; HL Deb 24 May 2004 vol 661 c436GC' name='column_436gc' href='#column_436gc' rel='bookmark'>436GC</a>
